data.description: Welcome to your new Home!  This home is a gorgeous 2 story with large entry foyer and an open staircase. This 5 bedroom, 4 bath home, has enormous amounts of natural light to make you feel right at home!  The main level of the home boasts of a large kitchen with plenty of storage and counter space, complete with a great breakfast nook area. The patio doors open to the private deck, patio, and hot tub area. There is also a large family room with fireplace.  Also adjoining the kitchen is the formal dining and living area. When entering from the garage, there is another bathroom/wash, and the laundry area on the main level of the home.  The upper level has a large landing area, with 3 bedrooms - including the Master Suite with a large walk-in closet, separate tub and shower, double sinks- and a lot of storage. Each of the bedrooms upstairs have their own walk-in closets. The finished basement has a family room, bathroom, and two additional bedrooms.  There is also ample storage and a separate mechanical room.  The in-floor heated triple stall garage also has 12 x 20 shop and/or storage area. The entire lawn has a zoned irrigation system. Contact Jeremy Horkey for your private viewing today.
